`createJWT` жҸҗдҫӣдәҶе®Ңж•ҙзҡ„ JWT зӯҫеҸ‘е’ҢйӘҢиҜҒеҠҹиғҪпјҢж”ҜжҢҒ HS256гҖҒRS256 зӯүз®—жі•гҖӮ

## еҹәжң¬з”Ёжі•

```typescript
import { createJWT } from "@aeron/auth";

const jwt = createJWT({
  secret: process.env.JWT_SECRET!,
  expiresIn: "7d",   // Token жңүж•Ҳжңҹ
  algorithm: "HS256" // й»ҳи®Өз®—жі•
});
```

## зӯҫеҸ‘ Token

```typescript
// зҷ»еҪ•и·Ҝз”ұ
router.post("/auth/login", async (ctx) => {
  const { email, password } = await ctx.body<{ email: string; password: string }>();

  const user = await findUserByEmail(email);
  if (!user || !await verifyPassword(password, user.passwordHash)) {
    throw new UnauthorizedError("йӮ®з®ұжҲ–еҜҶз Ғй”ҷиҜҜ");
  }

  // зӯҫеҸ‘ Token
  const token = await jwt.sign({
    sub: user.id,           // з”ЁжҲ· ID
    email: user.email,
    role: user.role,
  });

  return ctx.json({ token, expiresIn: "7d" });
});
```

## йӘҢиҜҒ Token

```typescript
// и®ӨиҜҒдёӯй—ҙд»¶
const authMiddleware: Middleware = async (ctx, next) => {
  const authHeader = ctx.headers.get("authorization");
  if (!authHeader?.startsWith("Bearer ")) {
    throw new UnauthorizedError("зјәе°‘и®ӨиҜҒ Token");
  }

  const token = authHeader.slice(7);

  try {
    const payload = await jwt.verify(token);
    ctx.state.user = payload;
  } catch (err) {
    throw new UnauthorizedError("Token ж— ж•ҲжҲ–е·ІиҝҮжңҹ");
  }

  await next();
};
```

## еҲ·ж–° Token

```typescript
// зӯҫеҸ‘еҲ·ж–° TokenпјҲжӣҙй•ҝжңүж•Ҳжңҹпјү
const accessToken = await jwt.sign({ sub: user.id, type: "access" }, { expiresIn: "15m" });
const refreshToken = await jwt.sign({ sub: user.id, type: "refresh" }, { expiresIn: "30d" });

// дҪҝз”ЁеҲ·ж–° Token иҺ·еҸ–ж–°зҡ„и®ҝй—® Token
router.post("/auth/refresh", async (ctx) => {
  const { refreshToken } = await ctx.body<{ refreshToken: string }>();

  const payload = await jwt.verify(refreshToken);
  if (payload.type !== "refresh") {
    throw new UnauthorizedError("ж— ж•Ҳзҡ„еҲ·ж–° Token");
  }

  const newAccessToken = await jwt.sign({ sub: payload.sub, type: "access" }, { expiresIn: "15m" });
  return ctx.json({ accessToken: newAccessToken });
});
```

## йқһеҜ№з§°еҠ еҜҶпјҲRS256пјү

дҪҝз”Ё RSA еҜҶй’ҘеҜ№пјҢйҖӮеҗҲеӨҡжңҚеҠЎд№Ӣй—ҙе…ұдә«йӘҢиҜҒпјҡ

```typescript
const jwt = createJWT({
  privateKey: process.env.JWT_PRIVATE_KEY!,  // з§Ғй’ҘпјҲзӯҫеҸ‘пјү
  publicKey: process.env.JWT_PUBLIC_KEY!,    // е…¬й’ҘпјҲйӘҢиҜҒпјү
  algorithm: "RS256",
  expiresIn: "1h",
});
