## JWT жҺҘеҸЈ

```typescript
interface JWTOptions {
  secret?: string;
  privateKey?: string;
  publicKey?: string;
  algorithm?: "HS256" | "HS384" | "HS512" | "RS256" | "RS384" | "RS512";
  expiresIn?: string | number;
}

interface JWT {
  sign(payload: Record<string, unknown>, options?: Partial<JWTOptions>): Promise<string>;
  verify<T = Record<string, unknown>>(token: string): Promise<T>;
  decode<T = Record<string, unknown>>(token: string): T | null;
}
```

`createAPIKeyManager` жҸҗдҫӣдәҶ API еҜҶй’Ҙзҡ„з”ҹжҲҗгҖҒйӘҢиҜҒе’Ңз®ЎзҗҶеҠҹиғҪпјҢйҖӮеҗҲдёәз¬¬дёүж–№ејҖеҸ‘иҖ…жҸҗдҫӣ API и®ҝй—®гҖӮ

## еҹәжң¬з”Ёжі•

```typescript
import { createAPIKeyManager } from "@aeron/auth";

const apiKeys = createAPIKeyManager({
  prefix: "ak",              // еҜҶй’ҘеүҚзјҖпјҡak_xxxx
  hashAlgorithm: "sha256",  // еӯҳеӮЁж—¶е“ҲеёҢ
});
```

## з”ҹжҲҗ API еҜҶй’Ҙ

```typescript
router.post("/api-keys", authMiddleware, async (ctx) => {
  const userId = ctx.state.user.sub;
  const { name, scopes } = await ctx.body<{ name: string; scopes: string[] }>();

  const { key, hash } = await apiKeys.generate();

  // еҸӘеӯҳеӮЁе“ҲеёҢеҖјпјҢдёҚеӯҳеӮЁеҺҹе§ӢеҜҶй’Ҙ
  await db.insert("api_keys", {
    user_id: userId,
    name,
    key_hash: hash,
    scopes: JSON.stringify(scopes),
    created_at: new Date(),
  }).execute();

  // еҸӘеңЁеҲӣе»әж—¶иҝ”еӣһдёҖж¬ЎеҺҹе§ӢеҜҶй’Ҙ
  return ctx.json({ key, name, scopes }, 201);
});
```

## йӘҢиҜҒ API еҜҶй’Ҙ

```typescript
const apiKeyAuth: Middleware = async (ctx, next) => {
  const key = ctx.headers.get("x-api-key");
  if (!key) {
    throw new UnauthorizedError("зјәе°‘ API еҜҶй’Ҙ");
  }

  const hash = apiKeys.hash(key);
  const apiKey = await db.from("api_keys")
    .where("key_hash", "=", hash)
    .where("revoked", "=", false)
    .first();

  if (!apiKey) {
    throw new UnauthorizedError("API еҜҶй’Ҙж— ж•Ҳ");
  }

  // жӣҙж–°жңҖеҗҺдҪҝз”Ёж—¶й—ҙ
  await db.update("api_keys")
    .set({ last_used_at: new Date() })
    .where("id", "=", apiKey.id)
    .execute();

  ctx.state.apiKey = apiKey;
  ctx.state.userId = apiKey.user_id;
  await next();
};
```

