  const id = ctx.headers.get("x-request-id") ?? randomUUID();
  ctx.state.requestId = id;
  ctx.responseHeaders.set("x-request-id", id);
  await next();
};
```

### й”ҷиҜҜеӨ„зҗҶдёӯй—ҙд»¶

